name: Thulough
content:
Thulough was a Rebel lieutenant intelligence officer who lived during the Galactic Civil War. He once went on a mission to Aurilia on the planet Dathomir. After the Battle of Yavin, he was tasked with capturing the Star Destroyer Blackguard from the traitorous Imperial Captain and self-proclaimed Grand Admiral Andal Sait.
Lieutenant Thulough was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Lieutenant Thulough was added to the game along with the "Star Destroyer" Heroic Encounter, introduced with the release of the "Chapter 8" update, on November 1, 2007.
